{"tid":1832164,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】武漢上車來港高鐵疑全停售　網站：沒相關班次","createTime":"2020-01-21T03:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T03:52:16.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c56500ac22aa89cab32f6ad72c30d0c1a05a24c5","tid":1832164,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:35:09.000Z","msg":"武漢的新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情持續擴散，截至今日（21日）早上8時，內地多個省市共錄得219宗個案。記者查看高鐵售票網包括中國鐵路12306網站、港鐵官網，發現由今日起，至到2月19日，沒有武漢來港高鐵班次車票發售，港鐵官網更彈出「沒有相關車次信息」。<br />\n<br />\n記者今早於12306網站搜尋今日由武漢來港的高鐵班次，雖然網站出示了兩趟列車，分別為G79和G305，但皆不供乘客購票。然而，同一班列車G79，由北京西來港的高鐵班次，則仍然有不同類型座位出售，換言之，班次仍如常營運，卻不停武漢站。<br />\n<br />\n現時不少港人會選擇到深圳北乘搭高鐵前往內地其他地點，內地現時仍有從深圳北開出的高鐵列車會停武漢。有乘客將於周四（23日）從深圳北出發，列車資料顯示將停武漢半小時。"},{"pid":"b658fc7e4f47b4d6a5da41c92ab632ab26b1ff0b","tid":1832164,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:35:42.000Z","msg":"要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6kBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=9b513e3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n而家美帝要求強国簽左第二階段先撤關稅<br />\n所以強国一定要被迫情況下同美帝簽協議<br />\n香港要搭順風車<br />\n<br />\n另外, 所羅門聯署:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fbeijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6kBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=4a500d02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again</a><br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"45ee3bf6fe629b10ca833439bd2482666a02c85f","tid":1832164,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:36:15.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f1b87f3a2de61f61eb755fa1edcacf5dd114bb99","tid":1832164,"uid":129169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:36:35.000Z","msg":"屍殺例車咁飛站"},{"pid":"e4478da589c064e78d0f456f1751a4c46cd8479c","tid":1832164,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6fc9d3900026322041fa9a293c6f4aec8e9c11","tid":1832164,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:37:48.000Z","msg":"無用，可以轉車，而且全支那已經有WARS"},{"pid":"4813a24084609a8dfc9e5c8173941cd4767fb260","tid":1832164,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:38:55.000Z","msg":"疫埠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上年封鎖鎮壓，今年封鎖自生自滅"},{"pid":"e4adecf2526fd6e3d0c29205a2dd0917176d9162","tid":1832164,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:39:14.000Z","msg":"武漢封鎖了 滅城了<br />\n帶病人民再沒生命是中共首要考慮"},{"pid":"53c6c5fa7bac6717cb83b332b685154db9436a30","tid":1832164,"uid":171668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:39:19.000Z","msg":"包唔撚住喇<br />\n好多7姑6一定仆翻上大陸<br />\n如果香港政府係香港人既政府<br />\n一早就應該宣布封鎖中國大陸所有對接口岸<br />\n所有中國飛機不得入境<br />\n香港人可以翻大陸，但翻左去就半年內不得入境香港<br />\n<br />\n敢唔敢做先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d41868831ce8c01b4919205b829ad3ce935f3e","tid":1832164,"uid